		<label>bulk kevlar / acrylic wool</label>
		<tab>AtlasMaterials</tab>
		<description>Develop techniques on the mass production of advanced plastic textiles, such as kevlar and acrylic wool. Overall taking less time and less materials to produce in the long term.</description>
